name: Yasmin Parry For President!
tagline: If not, what else do I have for this cheap domain?
body: ### Welcome to Yasmin Parry for President. I for one welcome our new overlord (and constitutionally problematical) President (to be) Yasmin. ### Control Z I made this cause I kinda promised that I would on our podcast Control Z. Check out the episode here: ### Why? What? Huh? Talk to us on Twitter: @will_ock or (the President to be) @yasminparry
